'''AS Rivière du Rempart''' is a [[Mauritius|Mauritian]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Mapou]], [[Rivière du Rempart District]]. They play in the [[Mauritian League|Mauritian Premier League]], the top division in Mauritian football.

They have never won the league or any domestic cups.

==Ground==
Their home stadium is [[Stade Anjalay]] (cap. 15,000) in [[Belle Vue Maurel]], [[Pamplemousses District]]. They share this stadium with [[Pamplemousses SC]].<ref>[http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/mauritius.shtml ASRR Stadium]</ref>

