'''Moussa Souleiman''' (born 1962) is a [[Djibouti]]an [[long-distance running|long-distance]] athlete.

Souleiman competed for his country at the [[1992 Summer Olympics]] held in [[Barcelona]], he entered the [[Athletics at the 1992 Summer Olympics – Men's 5000 metres|5000 metres]] where he came 13th in his heat so didn't qualify for the next round.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/so/moussa-souleiman-1.html Sports Reference Profile]</ref>

