The '''Penrith Ice Palace''' (also known as '''Penrith Ice Rink'''.) is an [[ice sports]] and public skate centre, located at the [[Penrith, New South Wales|Penrith]] precinct of [[Sydney]], in [[New South Wales]], [[Australia]]. It serves as the home ice rink of the Penrith Valley Figure Skating Club,<ref>{{cite web|title=Penrith Valley Figure Skating Club|url=http://www.penrithvalleyfigureskatingclub.com/|website=Penrith Valley Figure Skating Club|language=en}}</ref> [[Sydney Lightning]] and [[Sydney Maple Leafs]]. As of 2015 it is also the home ice rink of the [[Sydney Bears]] team for the [[Australian Ice Hockey League]] (AIHL).
